Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# The Great Division 大決裂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被深藏底處的秘密，超越我們掌握\NA secret has been hidden deep, beyond the grasp of all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}上頭卻要鎮壓我們，說他們會解決\NOur leaders have forbidden us, they say it will be solved
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不能眼睜睜看著我們被任由擺佈\NAnd I can't help but see the flaw in leaving us behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有什麼比蒙蔽整個國家還要更愚笨\NFor what's more foolish than to keep entire nations blind
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 導歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們保證你的安全\NWe will keep you safe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們維持國家運轉\NWe will run the race
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不用再多說了\NNothing left to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.27,0:01:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你沒其他選擇\NYou are here to stay
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我忍不了這種歧視\N一代一代的百般漠視\NCan't stand such isolation\NA stone cold shoulder for generations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他們虛假的甜言蜜語\N不斷傳入耳中\NThey whisper sweet little nothings\Ninto our gullible ears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我有件事想讓你知道\N請給我你們全部的注意力\NThere's something I should mention\NSo may I have all your attention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:02:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們來揭竿推翻這大決裂\NLet's reveal the great division
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們值得更多\N在這能夠有什麼未來？\NThere's more to be had\NWhat future do we have here?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}關於那堵牆外的景觀，大家眾說紛紜\NPlenty could be said about the sights beyond the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然我們的力量很小，卻能以量取勝\NThough little can be done for us, our numbers won't be small
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有人說我們本就應該成為傳說故事\NAnd some have told us we deserve to live as just a myth
